&lt;p&gt;Tatari is on a mission to revolutionize TV advertising. Founded in 2016 to help transform the antiquated world of TV advertising through the intelligent application of AI and machine learning, Tatari helps some of the world’s fastest growing brands including &lt;em&gt;Chime, Calm, Tecovas, Manscaped, Saatva, and Liquid I.V&lt;/em&gt;., reach their customers using linear and streaming TV ads. Our platform combines sophisticated media buying with proprietary analytics to turn TV advertising into an automated, digital-like experience, enabling businesses of any size to advertise on TV.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That approach has earned Tatari broad industry recognition, including being named&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tatari.tv/insights/tatari-named-best-ctv-adtech-platform-in-2025-martech-breakthrough-awards&quot;&gt;Best CTV AdTech Platform&lt;/a&gt; in the 8th annual &lt;em&gt;MarTech Breakthrough Awards&lt;/em&gt;, as well as honors from &lt;em&gt;Digiday&lt;/em&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tatari.tv/insights/tatari-awarded-best-ctv-ad-platform&quot;&gt;Best Connected TV Platform)&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;em&gt;AdExchanger&lt;/em&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tatari.tv/insights/tatari-wins-adexchangers-2023-most-innovative-tv-advertising-technology-award&quot;&gt;Most Innovative TV Advertising Technology&lt;/a&gt;), and &lt;em&gt;Business Insider &lt;/em&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tatari.tv/insights/business-insider-names-Tatari-a-2023-hottest-adtech-company&quot;&gt;Hottest AdTech Companies)&lt;/a&gt;. Tatari has also been recognized as the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tatari.tv/insights/inc-magazine-names-tatari-a-best-workplace-for-the-3rd-year-in-a-row&quot;&gt;Best Place to Work&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;em&gt;Inc. Magazine&lt;/em&gt;. Backed by an executive team of former founders and senior leaders from companies including Shazam, TrueCar, AdapTV, LiveRail, Amazon, Google, Meta, Microsoft, and Yahoo, Tatari continues to scale rapidly as TV advertising enters its next major era.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a “hunter” Account Executive to be part of the Client Development team to drive new business growth at Tatari. In this role, you will be integral to all stages of the sales cycle from initial strategy and pipeline generation to deal negotiation and close. The ideal candidate will have knowledge of both the TV advertising industry coupled with previous sales experience at a media or adtech company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive leads, grow the pipeline, push deal progression, and meet sales quotas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Focus on acquiring clients that are doing at least $10M in ARR, helping them transition or expand into TV advertising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the mindset of performance/growth marketers in order to deliver compelling sales presentations tailored to prospects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate business terms with decision-makers and executives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the Client Services and Media Buying teams to strategically support account growth–helping them transition or expand into TV advertising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate with Client Development leadership regarding pipeline, activities, customer needs, and other business opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years experience in B2B performance advertising sales (preferably linear or CTV)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated past success achieving revenue objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to tell a story with data, and clearly communicate technical terms and concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High motor to keep pace with fast moving clients to quickly grow the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of ownership, self-motivated, driven and able to work independently as well as fostering a collaborative environment&lt;/li&gt;
