&lt;p&gt;As a Convergent TV Planner, Strategy &amp;amp; Insights, you&#39;ll play a central role in shaping media strategy across the full client lifecycle — from competitive RFPs and new business pitches to scaling plans for existing clients and forward-looking scenarios that show brands exactly where they can grow and how to get there. In every case, your work starts with the audience, the data, and the &#39;why&#39; — and ends with a strategy that connects audience intelligence to measurable outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What sets this role apart is how you&#39;ll work. You&#39;ll bring together audience intelligence, competitive insights, and AI-powered tools to build strategies that go beyond channel selection and the platform, data, and support to back those recommendations.&lt;/p&gt;
