&lt;li&gt;Leverage Tatari&#39;s proprietary measurement tools alongside third-party audience platforms to identify where a client&#39;s target consumer actually watches, and build a media plan around that&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools to surface audience insights, identify patterns across campaigns, and pressure-test strategic assumptions — treating AI as a thinking partner, not just a production tool&lt;/li&gt;
